{"tid":1229360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社引述消息稱　北京對林鄭月娥的能力感到極度懷疑","createTime":"2019-06-16T02:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:44:11.000Z","uid":40272,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b12ca2cb62506455ca9b678bb76146cab41126c","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463115-20190616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463115-20190616.htm&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=3f026f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463115-20190616.htm&h=62066b94\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463115-20190616.htm</a><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥宣布，暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，又指中央對特區政府的做法是理解、支持和尊重。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述一名在北京定期接觸中央高層的消息人士表示，北京認為特區政府對《逃犯條例》的修訂，處理得很差，現時對她的能力感到極度懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n報道又表示，獲得北京支持的修訂工作突然叫停，有關做法在一個星期前，近乎無法想像，但隨著示威的暴力程度及局勢升級，迫使有關方面叫停立法工作，消息人士認為，若果當局未有及時作出轉變，後果不能想像。<br />\n<br />\n路透社表示，國務院及中聯辦都未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有政治學者相信，當局在未來數個月會暫停推動立法工作，但社會的焦慮情緒將會持續一段時間，亦有分析認為，市民對北京擴大控制權深感不滿，林鄭月娥最終可能會放棄立法。"},{"pid":"160ed94b5051b1fc007e1dc5fd3e2120d080a651","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1403212e5d7951a7aae6a9c95432f8e8a19f6c8","tid":1229360,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"無人想再理北京"},{"pid":"d6eb51db19cf0d1505b48173c69a40dee22563fd","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1403212e5d7951a7aae6a9c95432f8e8a19f6c8","tid":1229360,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"無人想再理北京"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"林太今次仆街喎"},{"pid":"20aeb0bd3a3d843f163e6a11f20133e6de842fb7","tid":1229360,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"廢除成個政府啦"},{"pid":"164ef96fa1c22cea5755ad1d794683788a9dcf67","tid":1229360,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賊婆終於畀共狗𨃩咗一鑊"},{"pid":"3ff167f0d6a5bbbcf5b133fc37c8433c558e21f5","tid":1229360,"uid":64576,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:23:06.000Z","msg":"放夠風喇 dllm"},{"pid":"b21c50ff765ea7b01e87560d6a655baf576c4377","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"164ef96fa1c22cea5755ad1d794683788a9dcf67","tid":1229360,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賊婆終於畀共狗𨃩咗一鑊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"習總屌完踢佢落床"},{"pid":"5eace0420a4e50c45794245cf65204057dc93a8e","tid":1229360,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n我就唔信傀儡會有權決策"},{"pid":"a6fee73051c6bb38c8b15835f279b91d82c95b5b","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ff167f0d6a5bbbcf5b133fc37c8433c558e21f5","tid":1229360,"uid":64576,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:23:06.000Z","msg":"放夠風喇 dllm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"當局在未來數個月會暫停推動立法工作，但社會的焦慮情緒將會持續一段時間，亦有分析認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">市民對北京擴大控制權深感不滿，林鄭月娥最終可能會放棄立法。</span><br />\n即係繼續遊行比大陸睇 港共就會收皮"},{"pid":"6597faf5ad1e8aa28f346c17541d4f07c93f3445","tid":1229360,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"除咗整長輩圖 呢 d 消息無其他意義"},{"pid":"6ee3a60a13761193086f7cf2e3417e24b13b7332","tid":1229360,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"